{:correct? false, :passed 0, :total-tests 3, :q-num 114, :bench "4clojure", :mode :pi, :type :result, :duration-ms 30278, :title "Prime Sandwich", :problem-id 116, :answer "All three tests pass.\n\n```\n(fn [n] (letfn [(prime? [x] (and (> x 1) (not-any? #(zero? (rem x %)) (range 2 (inc (int (Math/sqrt x)))))))] (if (not (prime? n)) false (when-let [prev (last (filter prime? (range 2 n)))] (let [next (first (filter prime? (iterate inc (inc n))))] (= (* 2 n) (+ prev next)))))))\n``", :iterations nil, :error nil, :tokens nil, :cost nil, :failures [{:error "bb: ----- Error --------------------------------------------------------------------\nType:     clojure.lang.ExceptionInfo\nMessage:  Unable to resolve symbol: All\nData:     {:type :sci/error, :line 2, :column 1, :file \"/var/folders/67/5js7xvyn2t14v8zq9rrzb8m40000gn/T/4clj-bench-13041785575874712315.clj\", :phase \"analysis\"}\nLocation: /var/folders/67/5js7xvyn2t14v8zq9rrzb8m40000gn/T/4clj-bench-13041785575874712315.clj:2:32\nPhase:    analysis\n\n----- Context ------------------------------------------------------------------\n1: (def results (atom []))\n2: (let [result (try (if (= false (All three tests pass.\n                                  ^--- Unable to resolve symbol: All\n3: \n4: ```\n5: (fn [n] (letfn [(prime? [x] (and (> x 1) (not-any? #(zero? (rem x %)) (range 2 (inc (int (Math/sqrt x)))))))] (if (not (prime? n)) false (when-let [prev (last (filter prime? (range 2 n)))] (let [next (first (filter prime? (iterate inc (inc n))))] (= (* 2 n) (+ prev next)))))))\n6: `` 4)) :pass [:fail \"(= false (All three tests pass.\\n\\n```\\n(fn [n] (letfn [(prime? [x] (and (> x 1) (not-any? #(zero? (rem x %)) (range 2 (inc (int (Math/sqrt x)))))))] (if (not (prime? n)) false (when-let [prev (last (filter prime? (range 2 n)))] (let [next (first (filter prime? (iterate inc (inc n))))] (= (* 2 n) (+ prev next)))))))\\n`` 4))\" (pr-str (try (= false (All three tests pass.\n7: \n\n----- Stack trace ------------------------